    "description": "<i>The Deckarium demo lets you play through about 25% of the game.</i><br><br>Deckarium is a deck-building pet simulator. Play pet cards to add to your terrarium or aquarium, and progress through levels to unlock new cards to add to your deck.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019910/extras/694a639e42f65598f2afaa2a7551541c.apng?t=1736996847\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019910/extras/694a639e42f65598f2afaa2a7551541c.poster.avif?t=1736996847\" class=\"bb_img\" width=90 height=75 /></picture></span><br><br>Keep your pets well fed and they'll produce coins for you. Some pets have bigger appetites than others! You will have to maintain the food-chain if you want to benefit from larger pets.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019910/extras/27700f685ada3eb939f4c61cb1c15cb1.apng?t=1736996847\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019910/extras/27700f685ada3eb939f4c61cb1c15cb1.poster.avif?t=1736996847\" class=\"bb_img\" width=500 height=100 /></picture></span><br><br>Your pets aren't the only ones who are hungry! Beware of ghosts who seek only to consume the souls of your pets!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019910/extras/581d64cbb21435d9b4abdaa6df001b6a.apng?t=1736996847\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019910/extras/581d64cbb21435d9b4abdaa6df001b6a.poster.avif?t=1736996847\" class=\"bb_img\" width=140 height=220 /></picture></span><br><br>Beat levels and minigames to earn extra currency for your own personal idle terrarium and vivarium, where you can collect and name your own unique pets without fear of phantoms!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019910/extras/07c97cd372bfa1a8d39bafa3c02248e5.apng?t=1736996847\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019910/extras/07c97cd372bfa1a8d39bafa3c02248e5.poster.avif?t=1736996847\" class=\"bb_img\" width=110 height=70 /></picture></span>",
